room_title: Escape room "Key of the Time" by WeXcape in Wichita
room_description:
In the year 2150, an unidentified flying object has crashed in a town in Kansas, a mysterious key appears above the crash site and collapsed the time dimension which spread throughout the surrounding area; expanding and preventing anything from getting near it.
You are the residents of the town that were thought to have been killed during the crash but you are not dead. Instead, you are trapped in the time before everything happened, you have to retrieve the key of time to set everything correct and avoid the disaster.
